message.content: cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.ET - This paper is likely to belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) category as it focuses on improving the efficiency and effectiveness of software testing. It may also belong to Programming Languages (cs.PL) as it discusses the use of theorem provers and heuristics in generating test cases. Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) is another possible category as the paper deals with avoiding redundancies in test cases. Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Emerging Technologies (cs.ET) are also possible categories as the paper discusses the use of smart sampling heuristics and specialized sub-sampling heuristics in generating test cases.
